      "content": "You're experiencing symptoms that could be due to heat exhaustion, but it's also possible you're dehydrated. Drink plenty of coconut water, but also consider taking a cool shower, lying down in the shade, and sipping on water regularly. If your symptoms persist, you might want to consider a more comprehensive approach to rehydration and rest. Just remember, if you feel worse, it's important to seek medical attention.",
      "source": "target",
